Class Role

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lafayette.server.domain.BaseDomainObject
      • org.lafayette.server.domain.Role
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DomainObject

    public class Role
extends BaseDomainObject
    Represents the roles a User has. This class represents the record sets which describes which user has what role.
    Author:
    Sven Strittmatter
